==Legacy==
In Amsterdam, there is a Max Euwe Plein (square) (near the Leidseplein) with a large chess set and statue, where the &#x27;Max Euwe Stichting&#x27; is located in a former jailhouse. It has a Max Euwe museum and a large collection of chess books.

==Honours==
* In 1936, Euwe was appointed Officer of the Order of Orange-Nassau.
* In 1979, Euwe was promoted to Commander of the Order of Orange-Nassau.

